<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7216> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7216" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor pro praetore. He was sent in 75, or more probably in 74, to Cyrene as quaestor pro praetore, or perhaps, like Cato to Cyprus in 58, as pro quaestore pro praetore to settle disturbed conditions in Cyrene (MRR 2.103; Oost, CPh 58, 1963, 11-25; Badian, JRS 55, 1965, 119-126; cf. J. M. Reynolds, JRS 52, 1962, 101). On his lineage, Sumner, Orators 92-93, 133, 141-143, with stemma, shows that the suggestion of Willems and Münzer (RE no. 238) identifying him with Lentulus Spinther (238), Cos. 57, is impossible." ;
	dprr:hasID 7216 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4415> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4415" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent as Quaestor, probably with imperium, to the province of Cyrene (Sall. Hist. 2.43M). See 75, note 4." ;
	dprr:hasID 4415 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4380> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4380" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent to Cyrene (Sall. Hist. 2.43M, in 75, Maurenbrecher, or 74, Münzer, RE)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4380 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4379> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4379" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "4 See Münzer (RE) on the question whether he should be identified with P. Cornelius Lentulus Spinther, Cos. 57, and (perhaps or) the P. Lentulus P. f. L. n,. Quaestor, who is named on coins of this period (Grueber, CRRBM 1.406)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4379 .
